In regardless of eddy diffusivity, the horizontal fluxes can be calculated using mass balance method by determining the balance of horizontal fluxes entering and leaving the desired virtual volume with source (Loubet et al. 2020). The fluxes (Fc) of a trace gas can be expressed as-7Fc=∫U.Cdx\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
